 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 5. the nigerian is not the person playing snooker##6
 6. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
