 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
 9. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
10. the farmhouse house is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
11. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
12. the person drinking juice is not the owner of the rabbit##6
13. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
14. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the craftsman house##8

